seo: 用友NC,任意文件上传,漏洞检测
seo_en: Yonyou NC, arbitrary file upload, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测用友NC系统的任意文件上传漏洞，通过构造特定的HTTP请求来验证是否存在该漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the arbitrary file upload vulnerability in Yonyou NC system by constructing specific HTTP requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
